text: LA-24 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Noreen Arif Khan of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Kutla in Muzaffarabad District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. Category:Muzaffarabad District ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016. Category:Government of Azad Kashmir Category:Constituencies of Pakistan
title: Constituency LA-24
